<h2>Schlein stage two hours after </h2>
The interview is Ferruccio de Bortoli. The focus is cheaper, but the ideas to refocus the duel do not lack. Progressivity of the IRS: "The more it contributes to the common good is a constitutional principle," says Schlein, who was inspired by de Bortoli. And if Schlein accuses the government to move forward only to hits of condones, favoring the "furbious and penalizing employees", Meloni claims to point to a whistle that "dyes a hand to citizens in difficulty", rejecting the accusations of "befriending evaders. The numbers don't say that. The 2023 was the record year in the recovery of tax evasion in Italy," emphasizes the premier. Schlein attacks on the <a href="https://www.agi.it/politica/news/2024-05-22/meloni-chiude-redditometro-26492145/">redditometro,</a> "a disaster" by "a confused government that first proposes and then takes a step back". Meloni assures that he has not changed his mind, "always contrary" to the income meter, but "there is a rule to guarantee the taxpayers, which does not give unlimited powers to the authorities".
&nbsp;
Before leaving the festival, Schlein reports to journalists what defines "the silence of the indecents". A film quote to say "believed that Meloni did not take the opportunity to say a word about the situation of Liguria and the arrest of Giovanni Toti. It is the silence of the indecent: Meloni undergoes the diktat of Salvini that asks Toti to resist, but who risks not to resist is the Liguria region". Even the premier does not spare the stylists towards the left, especially to detect "the disasters of the past" on the issue of wages. And to emphasize that "Tele Meloni is a fake news. At Tg1, I'm last in the standings compared to my predecessors from Renzi. The problem is, there's Telemeloni, but there's no Tele Pd anymore."
